title: Audiojack @ Square
content:
Thursday, 1st October, industry pioneers, AudioJack are firing up the dancefloor at Square. 

Ibiza based, Leeds bred, DJs, producers, record label owners and music enthusiasts, AudioJack always have fun-filled, energetic DJ sets. This is one of the reasons they have been enlisted to rock dancefloors at some of the world’s most respected clubs, including: Kater Holzig, Ritter Butzke & Watergate (Berlin), Sankeys (Ibiza), Rex Club (Paris), Hive (Zurich), Harry Klein (Munich), Electric Pickle (Miami), Fabric (London), Space (Ibiza) and many more. 

Night starts with Benni T’s debut at Square.  

H e is well known on the local scene among music aficionado and his sets are always full of charm and energy. 

Recharge with music!
